{"tid":2263652,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳宗憲打流感針後現不良反應　台醫生警告：快去急症室不是玩直播","createTime":"2020-10-30T05:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T07:29:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d232c6d3ee4ebc0814702039dfc8d452680b0fa1","tid":2263652,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:05:48.000Z","msg":"台灣藝人吳宗憲注射流感疫苗後，開直播表示自己第一次打流感疫苗，連續多日暈眩，還表示「本身抗體很好就不要假會」，後悔打了疫苗，態度遭台灣醫師批評「不懂不該帶風向」，而前台大感染科醫師孔祥琪則表示，症狀看起來有可能是中風，要吳不要再開直播，應該快去掛急診。<br />\n<br />\n孔祥琪也擔憂，流感疫苗已經注射多年，只要一有不良反應就會被放大檢視，引發很多人不敢打，擔心未來新冠肺炎疫苗上市後，這種情況會更嚴重，很多人都不敢打的結果，就是即使疫苗上市，還是沒有辦法解決大流行的問題。<br />\n<br />\n吳宗憲26日開直播透露去打了流感疫苗，打完就出現暈眩的狀況，已經3、4天，一直持續，有打電話回診所，告知自己的身體狀況，醫師讓他回診，但是因為工作太忙沒空，原本身體狀況很好，沒想到這次打完流感疫苗，身體竟然出現這樣巨大變化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201030/398822877115191296398602.jpeg/dAbOAJdXNMvT23Pkev15iuAv63SGm6omtbFbDbWxWw0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201030%2F398822877115191296398602.jpeg%2FdAbOAJdXNMvT23Pkev15iuAv63SGm6omtbFbDbWxWw0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=d9f266fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22f84fa2fd6f9ad359e163cb6f3fb4aba411a3e","tid":2263652,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"bbf5dfec8bb4d93e2ab3a26105a29f9ee95d0f45","tid":2263652,"uid":243084,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"快啲中風啦"},{"pid":"069db40e75353ba773b399c217fd29d305e8d854","tid":2263652,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"死唔去？"},{"pid":"2cd42e11e9903f65247e91c91740fe272778ff86","tid":2263652,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"支那憲叫黑箱車算啦"},{"pid":"4adf1c5da5954791b5229cc7bcd7db4a8b3ab0ca","tid":2263652,"uid":10056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"藝人係依D大事大非既情況下就會顯得好撚卑微同唔重要 然後又要出黎譁眾取寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c22df9de3d97b0caac940904a38481b362118e","tid":2263652,"uid":116896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"人地館長中槍開live係型<br />\n佢打針暈開live堅7"},{"pid":"32ff104f6e091b09300e2beb73921b29f3477051","tid":2263652,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"咁快去搵小鬼？"},{"pid":"b1e2da6067cccfb17942f084d1a59477574fb6f9","tid":2263652,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"去北京醫"},{"pid":"82de7dcaf0de4f4d8d30f99c6b3c3c4fb11b50c0","tid":2263652,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"台灣陳百祥 <br />\n支那憲"}]}